{"id": "1193907586735546479", "channel_id": "1193509262706618449", "type": 0, "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "刷新一下，歡迎有興趣補充的人來補充！", "timestamp": "2024-01-08T13:22:30.408000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193509262706618449", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "對於目前公關與營運方面的想法與建議。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1193759706741743786", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "挂一个技能。这个技能增加最大生命值，但是不会增加当前生命。凯科斯（粉鱼，反击鱼，狮子鱼）没有任何联动机制与最大生命值相关。也就是说，这个技能只是２费＋４点永久反击。很烂很没用的一个技能，强度与病症牌一般，而且每轮刷新。", "timestamp": "2024-01-08T03:34:53.070000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1193759706544615526", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1068518, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1188546911662252092/1193759706544615526/image.png?ex=69cc925d&is=69cb40dd&hm=9979595d6dfcd04d1de3d8a129359f689bc9d034a26083e37548422487d64dd9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1193775363462008882", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 19, "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "author_bot": false, "content": "嗷，這個我用過一段時間，那時候是帶打擊回15生命的那個命輪，因為沉戟看作打擊所以回得起來。當時猜測是防止奶量溢出？但也不太明白就當作角色機制沒有提問了。\n不過加最大生命值的關卡事件會同時回等量的血，只有凱刻斯加了上限但不回血，~~怎麼回事呢~~", "timestamp": "2024-01-08T04:37:05.923000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193759706741743786", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
